are interesting to you

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.220
and things that you think are
best for your product, best

00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:49.750
for your company, not
necessarily asking permission.

00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:53.220
We like to talk about seeing the
forest through the trees.

00:05:53.220 --> 00:05:55.990
Sort of novice engineers
get told what to do.

00:05:55.990 --> 00:05:57.800
They expect to get
told what to do.

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:59.030
They do exactly what
they're told.

00:05:59.030 --> 00:06:01.850
Then they come back and they
say, more work, please.

00:06:01.850 --> 00:06:05.050
