00:32:19.850 --> 00:32:20.570
BRYAN FITZPATRICK:
A lot faster.

00:32:20.570 --> 00:32:21.950
BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN:
Really visible.

00:32:21.950 --> 00:32:24.850
Defensive work is just as
