00:32:26.350 --> 00:32:28.590
Oh, we're gonna maintain
the product.

00:32:28.590 --> 00:32:30.000
We're gonna migrate
the database.

00:32:30.000 --> 00:32:30.790
BRYAN FITZPATRICK: Refactor--

00:32:30.790 --> 00:32:31.580
BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN: We're
