BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN:
Yeah, right.

00:32:56.600 --> 00:32:56.840
So--

00:32:56.840 --> 00:32:57.850
BRYAN FITZPATRICK: Right.

00:32:57.850 --> 00:32:59.330
Why didn't you write it
