It's like someone asks you to
do something that you can

00:33:54.520 --> 00:33:55.930
easily do--

00:33:55.930 --> 00:33:57.320
BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN: Or you
could easily say no.

00:33:57.320 --> 00:33:58.700
BRYAN FITZPATRICK: You can
easily say no, but it's

00:33:58.700 --> 00:34:01.010
