That's the corollary to this
theme is that it will destroy

00:34:57.110 --> 00:35:00.550
your karma and trust in this
favor economy if you leave and

00:35:00.550 --> 00:35:01.250
burn a bridge.

00:35:01.250 --> 00:35:02.390
