00:36:08.395 --> 00:36:08.670
BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN:
Who responds--

00:36:08.670 --> 00:36:09.005
BRYAN FITZPATRICK:
--a small test--

00:36:09.005 --> 00:36:09.730
BEN COLLINS-SUSSMAN: --to
an ad like that?

00:36:09.730 --> 00:36:09.980
Sorry.

00:36:09.980 --> 00:36:10.380
BRYAN FITZPATRICK: Yeah.

